                reliability, or suitability.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mt-10 mb-4">
                2. Critical Verification Requirement
            </h2>
            <p>
                While we test our calculation logic (such as leap years, weekday
                step distributions, and day count offsets) extensively to ensure
                high mathematical accuracy, date arithmetic can occasionally be
                impacted by localized browser runtime, daylight savings
                transitions, or configuration details.
            </p>
            <div
                class="bg-amber-50 border border-amber-200 text-amber-950 p-4 rounded-xl text-sm"
            >
                🔒 <strong>Required Safeguard:</strong> Any calculation result obtained
